{
  "texts": [
    "The map emerged through over 100 sessions of individual editing and facilitated (group) discussions, in which participants added over 1500 notes (virtual post-its) and other mindmap items.",
    "Participants frequently returned to the mind-map after their initial contribution, reacting to other participants' contributions.",
    "It is important to highlight that individual participants did not necessarily contribute equally to different parts of the mind-map.",
    "Moreover, in the course of the engagement process (5 months), the focus of the participants' activity-on the mind-map and their engagement with other stakeholders' input-shifted thematically across sections, with increasing attention to the identification of best practices towards the end of the engagement process.",
    "Throughout these activities, the moderator curated the map to increase readability, for instance by grouping thematically similar comments under a given thematic area of the board."
  ]
}